{"tid":45382,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"雲海: 尋日機場因電子紙條系統故障, 令控制塔曾未能處理部分離境航班資料","createTime":"2016-12-19T02:36:44.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-19T05:03:30.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"08b35fac3ab6d73c5f2b655f0da6038476194e80","tid":45382,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T02:36:44.000Z","msg":"雲海 陳雲海<br />\n47 mins &middot; <br />\n民航處自己證實，尋日下午約五時，控制塔未能處理部分離境航班資料，經調查後發現是電子紙條系統出現間歇性的短暫故障，電子紙條系統要re-boot，於下午六時十八分先回復正常運作。當局堅稱機場航班升降正常及航空安全沒有受到影響喎！"},{"pid":"497ca8192e9e6a45635abffffe9c6ad41660a118","tid":45382,"uid":18320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T02:39:14.000Z","msg":"屌你老母留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07ce9594b03e785e4a4bf7552fc023c1336dfbf5","tid":45382,"uid":6192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T02:44:38.000Z","msg":"明明新系統係好有問題<br />\n仲要死口唔識<br />\n搵埋黨報插人<br />\n係咪要出事先認呀"},{"pid":"dd46222deb3b5608fdb34b693fa8611c994c19a6","tid":45382,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T02:48:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>明明新系統係好有問題<br />\n仲要死口唔識<br />\n搵埋黨報插人<br />\n係咪要出事先認呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出左事都係員工唔跟程序做野, 人為疏忽<br />\n肯定唔關新系統事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bf73364cc0a3e2447884699fe5fda3d9b1ef673","tid":45382,"uid":54092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T03:18:53.000Z","msg":"只要唔認有問題， 就可過骨！<br />\n新香港管理方式！"},{"pid":"a6c6c711ba0eb2ccd092b93413840455eb98dd9e","tid":45382,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2